Description: Modern graphical package manager for Linux
 Apt-Ex Package Manager provides an intuitive, KDE Plasma 6-integrated
 interface for Linux package management. It features:
 .
  * APT package management with full support
  * High-performance LMDB caching for instant browsing
  * Category-based package navigation
  * Fast search across packages
  * Virtual scrolling for large package lists
  * Background operations with progress indicators
  * Plugin architecture for multiple backends
  * Native KDE Plasma 6 integration
